data.description: Ready for new owners, this unique 3 bedroom 2 bath home is one to see. Resting on a large, nearly 1 acre corner lot on Old Bethel, this home has a large deck off the back of the home, fenced back yard, and powered workshop. The possibilities are endless with this large property. Plenty of room for detached garage, mother in law suites, swimming pool and more! Inside you will find several living areas including the den, which is just off the kitchen and family room, a large entertainment room just past the kitchen, boasting vaulted ceilings and plenty of natural lighting; the family room, which could easily double as a formal dining area, has vaulted ceilings and a wood burning fire place. At this price, this one will not last long! Call today for your showing.
